---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Bridger by Levenhall — Market Entry Intelligence for US Federal Contracting" description="$760B in federal contracts a year. Bridger surfaces the work before the RFP, scores it against your profile, and stands watch after — built first for allied technology firms entering the US and for US tech companies capturing federal work.">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="b-hero">
        <div class="b-hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="b-hero-inner">
            <p class="b-hero-tag">A Levenhall Product</p>
            <div class="b-hero-brand">
                <img src="/images/products/bridger-mark.png" alt="" class="b-hero-mark" aria-hidden="true">
                <span class="b-hero-wordmark">Bridger</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="b-hero-h1">Market Entry Intelligence<br/>for US Federal Contracting.</h1>
            <p class="b-hero-tagline">$760B in federal contracts a year. Bridger surfaces the work before the RFP, scores it against your profile, and stands watch after &mdash; built first for allied technology firms entering the US and for US tech companies capturing federal work.</p>
            <div class="b-hero-cta">
                <a href="https://bridger.levenhall.com/get-started" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Request Access</a>
                <a href="https://bridger.levenhall.com/brief" class="btn btn-outline-white" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Read Today's Intel Brief</a>
            </div>
            <p class="b-hero-meta">Live at <a href="https://bridger.levenhall.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">bridger.levenhall.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── RIGHT NOW ON BRIDGER (STAT STRIP) ── -->
    <section class="b-live">
        <div class="b-live-inner">
            <p class="b-live-label">Right now on Bridger</p>
            <div class="b-live-stats">
                <div class="b-stat"><span class="b-stat-val">$760<span class="b-u">B</span></span><span class="b-stat-lbl">Annual federal contracts</span></div>
                <div class="b-stat"><span class="b-stat-val">2,300<span class="b-u">+</span></span><span class="b-stat-lbl">Signals indexed this week</span></div>
                <div class="b-stat"><span class="b-stat-val">1,400<span class="b-u">+</span></span><span class="b-stat-lbl">Allied tech firms</span></div>
                <div class="b-stat"><span class="b-stat-val">60<span class="b-u">+</span></span><span class="b-stat-lbl">Countries represented</span></div>
                <div class="b-stat"><span class="b-stat-val">40<span class="b-u">+</span></span><span class="b-stat-lbl">Live sources</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── OPENING ── -->
    <section class="b-opening">
        <div class="b-prose reveal">
            <p class="b-lede">Most platforms tell you what already happened. Bridger sees the work before SAM.gov publishes it.</p>
            <p>Appropriations bills, committee markups, agency forecasts, GAO bid protests, OFAC entity-list updates &mdash; the signal that decides who wins moves six to twelve months ahead of the RFP. Bridger indexes the signal, scores every opportunity against your profile, and gives a <strong>GO / MONITOR / NO-GO</strong> verdict overnight.</p>
            <p>Then it stands watch: forty automated jobs a day, running while you sleep.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── WHO IT'S FOR ── -->
    <section class="b-who">
        <div class="b-who-inner">
            <header class="b-who-head reveal">
                <span class="b-eyebrow b-eyebrow-light">§ Who Bridger is for</span>
                <h2>Three sides. One platform.</h2>
            </header>
            <div class="b-who-grid reveal">
                <a href="https://bridger.levenhall.com/for-tech-companies" class="b-who-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <span class="b-who-num">01</span>
                    <h3>Tech Companies</h3>
                    <p>Allied firms from AUKUS, Five Eyes, and NATO nations entering the US. US tech companies capturing federal work. Appropriations signal, pre-RFP scoring, competitor reconstruction, and the compliance layer &mdash; ITAR, FOCI, CFIUS, DSGL, DISP &mdash; that no other platform touches.</p>
                    <span class="b-who-cta">How tech companies use Bridger &rarr;</span>
                </a>
                <a href="https://bridger.levenhall.com/for-providers" class="b-who-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <span class="b-who-num">02</span>
                    <h3>Service Providers</h3>
                    <p>Compliance advisors, proposal writers, US incorporation specialists, 8(a) JV partners, contract manufacturers. Free listing. Inbound leads at the point of intent. 10% commission on completed engagements via Stripe Connect.</p>
                    <span class="b-who-cta">How providers use Bridger &rarr;</span>
                </a>
                <a href="https://bridger.levenhall.com/for-lobbyists" class="b-who-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <span class="b-who-num">03</span>
                    <h3>Lobbyists</h3>
                    <p>Government-relations firms writing policy briefings on appropriations, defense, and tech trade. Free listing. 15% commission on engagements.</p>
                    <span class="b-who-cta">How lobbyists use Bridger &rarr;</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── STANDING WATCH ── -->
    <section class="b-watch">
        <div class="b-watch-grid">
            <aside class="b-watch-rail reveal">
                <span class="b-eyebrow">§ Standing Watch</span>
                <h2>Forty automated jobs a day.<br/>You get one page.</h2>
                <p class="b-watch-lede">Watches run in the background across appropriations, awards, deadlines, competitors, programs, and countries. What lands in your morning brief is what actually moved.</p>
            </aside>
            <div class="b-watch-body">
                <article class="b-watch-item reveal">
                    <span class="b-watch-num">01</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Morning Intelligence Brief</h3>
                        <p>Tailored to your profile, delivered at 6 AM Eastern. Overnight signal condensed into what deserves the first hour of your day.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="b-watch-item reveal">
                    <span class="b-watch-num">02</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Deadline Watch</h3>
                        <p>14, 7, 3, 1 days. The pipeline you are actually pursuing, held against the clock.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="b-watch-item reveal">
                    <span class="b-watch-num">03</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Competitor Watch</h3>
                        <p>Awards, value jumps, recompetes, agency moves. Every incumbent, reconstructed from public records and watched for movement.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="b-watch-item reveal">
                    <span class="b-watch-num">04</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Program Watch</h3>
                        <p>Funding moves, forecast shifts, new solicitations against the programs of record you care about.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="b-watch-item reveal">
                    <span class="b-watch-num">05</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Country Watch</h3>
                        <p>Instability tracking on the countries where your supply chain, partners, or opportunities sit.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="b-watch-item reveal">
                    <span class="b-watch-num">06</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Analyst Desk</h3>
                        <p>Instant AI response or human analyst, on demand. Ask, and get the answer inside the platform.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── BRIDGER STAFF ── -->
    <section class="b-staff">
        <div class="b-staff-inner">
            <header class="b-staff-head reveal">
                <span class="b-eyebrow b-eyebrow-light">§ Bridger Staff</span>
                <h2>Six officers on the cycle.</h2>
                <p class="b-staff-lede">On <strong>Pathfinder Agentic ($1,499/mo)</strong> Bridger runs a six-officer staff against your pipeline &mdash; briefing, capture, entry, profile, marketplace, and briefing officers, drafting the work you would draft. Nothing submits, sends, or files without your click.</p>
            </header>
            <div class="b-staff-grid reveal">
                <div class="b-officer">
                    <span class="b-officer-role">Intelligence Officer</span>
                    <p>Assembles the 6 AM briefing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="b-officer">
                    <span class="b-officer-role">Capture Officer</span>
                    <p>Drafts bid / no-bid analysis.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="b-officer">
                    <span class="b-officer-role">Allied-Entry Officer</span>
                    <p>Maps US-entry pathways for allied firms.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="b-officer">
                    <span class="b-officer-role">Profile Officer</span>
                    <p>Watches SAM, FPDS, CMMC posture.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="b-officer">
                    <span class="b-officer-role">Marketplace Officer</span>
                    <p>Drafts replies to inbound demand.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="b-officer">
                    <span class="b-officer-role">Briefing Officer</span>
                    <p>Drafts policy and program briefings.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ── -->
    <section class="b-cta">
        <div class="b-cta-glow"></div>
        <div class="b-cta-inner">
            <div class="b-cta-rule"></div>
            <p class="b-cta-eyebrow">Live Now &middot; v2026.06</p>
            <h2>Open Bridger.</h2>
            <p>Production at bridger.levenhall.com. The daily brief is free and public. Scout tier free; Pathfinder Agentic unlocks the officer stack and the full watch cycle.</p>
            <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
                <a href="https://bridger.levenhall.com/get-started" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Request Access</a>
                <a href="https://bridger.levenhall.com/brief" class="btn btn-outline-white" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Daily Brief</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* ── HERO ── */
    .b-hero {
        background:
            radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.06), transparent 70%),
            #060c18;
        padding: var(--s-16) var(--s-3) var(--s-12);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .b-hero-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%; left: 50%;
        width: 720px; height: 720px;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.14) 0%, transparent 60%);
        filter: blur(48px);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .b-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
        opacity: 0.45;
    }

    .b-hero-inner {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .b-hero-tag {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.66rem;
        letter-spacing: 3.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-5);
    }

    .b-hero-brand {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--s-3);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-6);
    }

    .b-hero-mark {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 0 24px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25));
    }

    .b-hero-wordmark {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: #fff;
        letter-spacing: -1.5px;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .b-hero-h1 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.9rem);
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
        letter-spacing: -0.8px;
    }

    .b-hero-tagline {
        font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        line-height: 1.75;
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-5);
    }

    .b-hero-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--s-2);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
    }

    .b-hero-meta {
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }
    .b-hero-meta a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── LIVE STATS ── */
    .b-live {
        background: #0a1628;
        padding: var(--s-6) 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15);
    }

    .b-live-inner {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .b-live-label {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.66rem;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .b-live-stats {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
        gap: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .b-stat {
        padding: var(--s-4) var(--s-2);
        text-align: center;
        border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .b-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .b-stat-val {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.9rem;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .b-u {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--gold);
    }

    .b-stat-lbl {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.68rem;
        letter-spacing: 1.3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* ── SHARED ── */
    .b-eyebrow {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 2.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
    }

    .b-eyebrow-light { color: var(--gold); }

    .b-opening h2,
    .b-who h2,
    .b-watch h2,
    .b-staff h2,
    .b-cta h2,
    .b-lede {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    /* ── OPENING ── */
    .b-opening {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .b-prose {
        max-width: 660px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .b-lede {
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-5);
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
    }

    .b-opening p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
    }

    .b-opening strong {
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* ── WHO ── */
    .b-who {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a1628 0%, var(--deep-navy) 100%);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
        position: relative;
    }

    .b-who::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25);
    }

    .b-who-inner {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .b-who-head {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-10);
    }

    .b-who-head h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 2.6rem);
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .b-who-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        grid-auto-rows: 1fr;
        gap: var(--s-3);
    }

    .b-who-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
        padding: var(--s-5);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--s-3);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .b-who-card:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    }

    .b-who-num {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        color: var(--gold);
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .b-who-card h3 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
    }

    .b-who-card p {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        margin: 0;
        flex: 1;
    }

    .b-who-cta {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-top: auto;
    }

    /* ── WATCH ── */
    .b-watch {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .b-watch-grid {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.4fr;
        gap: var(--s-10);
        align-items: start;
    }

    .b-watch-rail {
        position: sticky;
        top: 100px;
        padding-right: var(--s-3);
    }

    .b-watch-rail h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
        line-height: 1.15;
    }

    .b-watch-lede {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--text-medium);
    }

    .b-watch-item {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
        gap: var(--s-4);
        padding-bottom: var(--s-4);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.08);
    }

    .b-watch-item:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }

    .b-watch-num {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        color: var(--gold);
        line-height: 1;
        padding-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    .b-watch-item h3 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }

    .b-watch-item p {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── STAFF ── */
    .b-staff {
        background: #0a1628;
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
        position: relative;
    }

    .b-staff::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25);
    }

    .b-staff-inner {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .b-staff-head {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-8);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .b-staff-head h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 2.6rem);
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
    }

    .b-staff-lede {
        font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .b-staff-lede strong {
        color: var(--gold);
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .b-staff-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: var(--s-3);
    }

    .b-officer {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border-left: 3px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.5);
        padding: var(--s-4) var(--s-4);
    }

    .b-officer-role {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .b-officer p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .b-cta {
        background:
            radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08), transparent 70%),
            #060c18;
        padding: var(--s-14) var(--s-3);
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .b-cta-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%; left: 50%;
        width: 600px; height: 600px;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
        filter: blur(40px);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .b-cta::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
    }

    .b-cta-inner {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .b-cta-rule {
        width: 32px; height: 1px;
        background: var(--gold);
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-4);
    }

